'''西直门外大街'''是[[北京市|北京市]][[西城區|西城區]]的一条重要道路，因位在[[西直门|西直门]]外故称西直门外大街。位于[[西城区|西城区]]西北部，大部分位于[[展览路街道|展览路街道]]辖区内，但白石新桥至三里河路北口一段属[[海淀区|海淀区]]。东起[[西直门桥|西直门桥]]，西至[[中关村大街|白石桥路]]。有[[北京展览馆|北京展览馆]]<ref>{{Cite web|url =http://www.expo-china.com/pages/hall/200311/58/index.shtml|title =北京展览馆|accessdate =2015-12-18|archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20160308001323/http://www.expo-china.com/pages/hall/200311/58/index.shtml|archivedate =2016-03-08|deadurl =yes}}</ref>、[[北京动物园|北京动物园]]<ref>{{Cite web|url =http://m.city8.com/bj/chuxingfuwu/M555167_WIIY|title =北京动物园馆|access-date =2015-12-18|archive-date =2019-08-21|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20190821090925/http://m.city8.com/bj/chuxingfuwu/M555167_WIIY|dead-url =no}}</ref>、[[北京天文館|北京天文館]]<ref>{{Cite web|url =https://www.google.com.tw/search?q=%E8%A5%BF%E7%9B%B4%E9%96%80%E5%A4%96%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%97%E7%9A%84%E6%99%AF%E9%BB%9E&npsic=0&rflfq=1&tbm=lcl&ved=0ahUKEwiwgp778uXJAhVnGaYKHcq_B38Q0CcILQ&rlfi=hd:;si:&tbs=lf_msr:-1,lf:1,lf_ui:1&oll=39.93809050361607,116.33919100000003&ospn=0.003948581824403163,0.00996708869934082&oz=17&fll=39.93814808707693,116.34099344445804&fspn=0.003948578501841382,0.010149478912353516&fz=17&ei=fz10VvDGMeeymAXK_574Bw&qop=1|title= 西直門外大街的景點}}</ref>等景點。

2001年[[2001年夏季世界大學運動會|北京大运会]]开幕前，西外大街经历了大规模改扩建，在白石桥和北京展览馆设置了两座路堑式立交<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.chinanews.com/2001-08-09/26/112144.html|title=京城西北路网即将贯通 将作大运村主干道|publisher=[[中国新闻社|中国新闻社]]|date=2001-08-09|accessdate=2021-05-12|archive-date=2021-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512084657/https://www.chinanews.com/2001-08-09/26/112144.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但白石桥迤东至北展桥段没有设计非机动车道，以防非机动车与快速路机动车混行，过境非机动车需绕行南侧的[[西直门外南路|西直门外南路]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://auto.sina.com.cn/news/2001-08-09/12520.shtml|title=学院路通车西外大街改造 西直门该怎么走|work=[[北京青年报|北京青年报]]|date=2001-08-09|accessdate=2021-05-12|archive-date=2021-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512032046/https://auto.sina.com.cn/news/2001-08-09/12520.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，直至2020年11月20日西外大街双向复设非机动车道<ref>{{cite news|url=http://beijing.qianlong.com/2020/1120/5025652.shtml|title=动物园门前有了“骑行红毯”|work=[[北京日报|北京日报]]|date=2020-11-20|accessdate=2021-05-12|archive-date=2021-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512134529/http://beijing.qianlong.com/2020/1120/5025652.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

